Package: rtide
Title: Tide Heights and Timings
Version: 0.0.3.9001
Date: 2017-04-06
Authors@R: c(
    person("Joe", "Thorley", email = "joe@poissonconsulting.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Luke", "Miller", email = "contact@lukemiller.org", role = "aut"))
Description: Calculates tide heights, and the timing of slack tides, 
    based on tide station harmonics and offsets for 3,042 NOAA tide stations.
URL: https://github.com/poissonconsulting/rtide
BugReports: https://github.com/poissonconsulting/rtide/issues
